# Large source media files — GitHub blocks anything over 100 MB and warns
# over 50 MB. These are the unoptimized source masters; only the
# web-encoded `*-web.mp4` versions are committed and shipped to the site.
# Originals stay on disk locally for re-encoding, never enter git.
/public/hero/waveshero.mp4
/public/hero/trade.mp4
/public/hero/waves.mp4
/public/hero/waves-loop.mp4
/public/hero/about.mp4
/public/hero/about-story.mp4
